				h2 About
				p The Datavore<sup>&reg;</sup> team has deep domain expertise in databases, time series, and analytics with a successful track record of building technology within the financial services sector. The team has experience working at companies including Goldman Sachs, Citigroup, UBS, Thomson Reuters, Ernst & Young, and KPMG.
